    {
      "id": "note_1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1130,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#8892b0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": ["notes"],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1601,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1601,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. VOICE-CENTRIC — The orb IS the app. Everything\n   else is secondary to the voice interaction.\n\n2. ALIVE — Background gradient shifts with state.\n   The orb breathes, pulses, and glows.\n\n3. IMMERSIVE — No top app bar stealing space.\n   Full-screen dark canvas. Content floats.\n\n4. GLASS-MORPHISM — Message cards use frosted\n   glass effect over the dark background.\n\n5. WARM — Deep navy (not flat black), indigo\n   accents, coral for action. Feels like a\n   cozy room, not a cold terminal.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. VOICE-CENTRIC — The orb IS the app. Everything\n   else is secondary to the voice interaction.\n\n2. ALIVE — Background gradient shifts with state.\n   The orb breathes, pulses, and glows.\n\n3. IMMERSIVE — No top app bar stealing space.\n   Full-screen dark canvas. Content floats.\n\n4. GLASS-MORPHISM — Message cards use frosted\n   glass effect over the dark background.\n\n5. WARM — Deep navy (not flat black), indigo\n   accents, coral for action. Feels like a\n   cozy room, not a cold terminal.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "note_2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 600,
      "y": 1130,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#8892b0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": ["notes"],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1602,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1602,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "KEY CHANGES FROM CURRENT DESIGN:\n\n- Remove TopAppBar → floating minimal header\n- Background: #121212 (flat) → #0A0E27 (rich navy)\n- Primary: #1A73E8 (Google blue) → #4C3BCF (warm indigo)\n- Orb: 3 flat circles → 4-layer gradient with glow\n- FAB → Centered circular call button\n- Message bubbles → Glass cards with subtle border\n- Error red → Soft coral #FF6B6B\n- Add call timer when active\n- Add search to History screen\n- Add time grouping (Today/Yesterday) to History\n- Conversation cards show preview + message count",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "KEY CHANGES FROM CURRENT DESIGN:\n\n- Remove TopAppBar → floating minimal header\n- Background: #121212 (flat) → #0A0E27 (rich navy)\n- Primary: #1A73E8 (Google blue) → #4C3BCF (warm indigo)\n- Orb: 3 flat circles → 4-layer gradient with glow\n- FAB → Centered circular call button\n- Message bubbles → Glass cards with subtle border\n- Error red → Soft coral #FF6B6B\n- Add call timer when active\n- Add search to History screen\n- Add time grouping (Today/Yesterday) to History\n- Conversation cards show preview + message count",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

